'''Ducha''' was a nobility title in the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]] and oversaw regions in the [[Hapes Cluster/Legends|Hapes Cluster]].

The Ducha [[AlGray]] controlled the [[Relephon Moons]], while the Ducha [[Galney (Ducha of Terephon)|Galney]] ruled on the world of [[Terephon]]. It is not known what sort of powerbase Ducha [[Requud]] had, but like the other two Duchas, she commanded her own combat fleet, consisting of [[Hapan Battle Dragon|Battle Dragons]] and other warships.

Reflecting the matriarchal nature of Hapan society, all three known Duchas were female. The title of [[Duch'da]] may have denoted a Ducha's heir.

